NAME
    Template::Plugin::Komma - TT2 plugin to commify numbers (German format)

SYNOPSIS
      [% USE Komma %]
      Prozent:   [% 12.3    | komma %] %
      Einwohner: [% 1200000 | komma0 %]
      Preis:     [% 44.9    | komma2 %] EUR

      # Output:
      Prozent:   12,3 %
      Einwohner: 1.200.000
      Preis      44,90 EUR

DESCRIPTION
    This plugin is the German version of Template::Plugin::Comma. It
    installs 3 filters: "komma", "komma0" and "komma2".

    "komma" outputs the number with ',' as decimal point and '.' as thousand
    separator.

    "komma0" rounds the number to an integer and outputs the number with
    thousend separators.

    "komma2" rounds the number to 2 digits after the point
    (Nachkommastellen).

NOTE
    The interface is a little bit different to Template::Plugin::Comma,
    "komma" expects a number as parameter ("comma" can be feeded with a
    whole line of text and only the numbers are converted.)

